  "method": [
    "Bring 3 cups of water to a boil in a medium saucepan. Add the cereal, cinnamon, and salt. Reduce the heat to medium low and cover. Cook for 8 minutes, stirring occasionally, until all the water is absorbed. Stir in peanut butter and coconut cream.",
    "Serve in two bowls and garnish with the cranberries, pecans, hempseed, and maple syrup."
